<!----------------------->
<scan style="font-family: 'Georgia'; font-variant: small-caps; font-size: 80%; font-weight: bold; margin: 0 0 0.625% 0; padding:0; border:0; line-height:70%">Dec 2022- </scan><strong>Recent Posts.</strong> <br> See our most recent posts on covered bonds:<br>
<ul>
	<li><a href="http://www.us-covered-bonds.com/2020/02/14/videos/">See new videos on covered bonds.</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://www.us-covered-bonds.com/2022/12/26/resiliency-of-canadian-covered-bonds/">Resiliency of Canadian Covered Bonds</a></li>
